{"tid":127632,"cid":25,"subCid":0,"title":"我主人出街成日搶繩","createTime":"2017-02-20T08:31:51.000Z","updateTime":"2017-02-22T10:20:14.000Z","uid":49031,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"8ec6bdfa2ba6d5d2d6b0d0f8d190caaa660214cc","tid":127632,"uid":49031,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-20T08:31:51.000Z","msg":"點教好 ？<br />\n用左好多方法都冇乜效"},{"pid":"6692e30738215205ba5a29748ac9eda8b73937bd","tid":127632,"uid":59408,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-20T11:21:25.000Z","msg":"借 post問埋， 收養咗隻唐狗六個月左右大，第一次上繩，即刻變左癲狗咁，狂哀號喊叫，好似昇龍拳咁旋轉狂跳，最後我屈服左除返佢，之後怕咗我，又避我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7f0e93585d73dc662e56758ed393f04ee8b42f4d","tid":127632,"uid":67036,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-20T15:34:45.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>借 post問埋， 收養咗隻唐狗六個月左右大，第一次上繩，即刻變左癲狗咁，狂哀號喊叫，好似昇龍拳咁旋轉狂跳，最後我屈服左除返佢，之後怕咗我，又避我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n你唔可以屈服架 咁樣佢更加一見到狗繩就怕左唔敢出街 <br />\n六個月大你用胸帶等佢冇咁驚先 <br />\n或者你試下用零食引下佢 慢慢引佢上繩 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f499e417757a8bb4fd5b6c02f998ae94ff515849","tid":127632,"uid":67036,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-20T15:45:06.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>點教好 ？<br />\n用左好多方法都冇乜效</blockquote><br />\n佢搶繩你由佢搶 但你唔好行 搶到佢停左先繼續行<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fc1faa15a2764b19968cec10dffb0188bca53fe8","tid":127632,"uid":49031,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-20T17:28:40.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>點教好 ？<br />\n用左好多方法都冇乜效</blockquote><br />\n佢搶繩你由佢搶 但你唔好行 搶到佢停左先繼續行<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n上網睇 又要轉身又剩<br />\n我試左好多次唔行 佢都識坐低 但無限loop <br />\n始終令唔到主人跟住我<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/18.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"67bbef5e410242d1d0a8ea4c8126e649acaf1258","tid":127632,"uid":9412,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-20T17:34:05.000Z","msg":"我果隻驚想走佬先會搶<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8732fdd0c13b5524b6e773fd38052312f4670681","tid":127632,"uid":34993,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-20T17:48:02.000Z","msg":"睇dogwhisper啦"},{"pid":"2303e4be0b0f3285aedc5a30c5facced89647e02","tid":127632,"uid":65381,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-20T17:57:57.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>點教好 ？<br />\n用左好多方法都冇乜效</blockquote><br />\n佢搶繩你由佢搶 但你唔好行 搶到佢停左先繼續行<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我都係用依個方法<br />\n而家主人冇再搶繩"},{"pid":"8f45094d43684bda53aecc689d12419f4e3d31bd","tid":127632,"uid":49031,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-20T18:23:11.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>睇dogwhisper啦</blockquote><br />\n有睇呀 佢主要教mentally 控制隻狗<br />\n好深奧<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/03.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"05a7e5bd45aa76383f61d67dc51fc86f2c41f14b","tid":127632,"uid":44897,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-21T06:05:01.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>睇dogwhisper啦</blockquote><br />\n有睇呀 佢主要教mentally 控制隻狗<br />\n好深奧<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/03.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n你要行係隻狗前面，等佢跟你行<br />\n<br />\n佢搶行前因為佢來lead 你， 所以唔可以俾佢成功"},{"pid":"08d0f6711565141bef28229da6dcd5bd7d778845","tid":127632,"uid":49031,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-21T08:45:09.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>睇dogwhisper啦</blockquote><br />\n有睇呀 佢主要教mentally 控制隻狗<br />\n好深奧<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/03.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n你要行係隻狗前面，等佢跟你行<br />\n<br />\n佢搶行前因為佢來lead 你， 所以唔可以俾佢成功</blockquote><br />\n反而想知有咩實際行動做到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6707fbfcd2d41c0a900129fec9908f19ddcf6d65","tid":127632,"uid":7416,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-21T12:47:07.000Z","msg":"同問 我隻狗5個月大 呢排打齊哂針帶佢落街 佢都唔係好肯行 我冇專登扯佢 純粹跟住佢 但佢行得幾步又停 係咁食地下啲葉呀草呀 都唔知點好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5332e0645bdbe49862302da5c55767d17f200da1","tid":127632,"uid":71655,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-21T12:49:25.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"e85953ddbddfea97f7a616462671cea8e97bba88","tid":127632,"uid":71655,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-21T12:49:47.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"1a8c3a511fe484a5c78ad5c4fb8c5bb47a50142d","tid":127632,"uid":7416,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-21T12:50:34.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>同問 我隻狗5個月大 呢排打齊哂針帶佢落街 佢都唔係好肯行 我冇專登扯佢 純粹跟住佢 但佢行得幾步又停 係咁食地下啲葉呀草呀 都唔知點好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n專登扯佢 LO</blockquote><br />\n點都有扯下佢行喇緊係 但佢死都唔郁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"25d82d9cad251fbee814aaa293f112a113da5289","tid":127632,"uid":44897,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-22T01:56:18.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>睇dogwhisper啦</blockquote><br />\n有睇呀 佢主要教mentally 控制隻狗<br />\n好深奧<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/03.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n你要行係隻狗前面，等佢跟你行<br />\n<br />\n佢搶行前因為佢來lead 你， 所以唔可以俾佢成功</blockquote><br />\n反而想知有咩實際行動做到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n拉緊啲條狗帶，等佢貼你腳邊行<br />\n唔洗怕拉親佢，就到㗎"},{"pid":"cac97855c2f24b6b839a014de1650084b8478222","tid":127632,"uid":36169,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-22T02:59:38.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>同問 我隻狗5個月大 呢排打齊哂針帶佢落街 佢都唔係好肯行 我冇專登扯佢 純粹跟住佢 但佢行得幾步又停 係咁食地下啲葉呀草呀 都唔知點好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n專登扯佢 LO</blockquote><br />\n點都有扯下佢行喇緊係 但佢死都唔郁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n你帶佢嘅時候，唔好在意佢，自己行自己就可以，你太在意佢，佢feel到，情況好似一個要睇玩具嘅小朋友，你唔停低，佢連出聲喊嘅機會都無就過左，所以變左佢hold你咁"},{"pid":"95ee1e5b8a0bc06d80f4582b024815d5a17c5edc","tid":127632,"uid":61620,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-22T04:01:45.000Z","msg":"可以試下用easywalk 再孖繩出街"},{"pid":"64f80aa15bef6e6a8ec28f11952e3a8488eae261","tid":127632,"uid":49031,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-22T07:45:33.000Z","msg":"我諗住淘條口繩<br />\n係咪好多餘？"},{"pid":"c148d8387decbdb63077d27a8c23913c5eeac040","tid":127632,"uid":38898,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-22T07:50:01.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我諗住淘條口繩<br />\n係咪好多餘？</blockquote><br />\n其實呢隻繩先岩用來訓練"},{"pid":"630f1ae971d68e92bf73c609c2fd331da2e62ee5","tid":127632,"uid":49031,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-22T10:20:14.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>我諗住淘條口繩<br />\n係咪好多餘？</blockquote><br />\n其實呢隻繩先岩用來訓練</blockquote><br />\n咁我淘條玩下"}]}